theorem closure_interior_idempotent_six {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior A)))))))))) =
      closure (interior A) := by
  simp [Topology.closure_interior_idempotent]

theorem closure_interior_idempotent_six {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure A))))))))) =
      closure (interior A) := by
  simp [Topology.closure_interior_idempotent]

theorem interior_closure_interior_eq_interior_of_isOpen
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} (hA : IsOpen (A : Set X)) :
    interior (closure (interior (A : Set X))) = interior (closure A) := by
  simpa [hA.interior_eq]
